column4: Oh no, I forgot to buy an After Pill! What now?
Ugh... Looks like I will have to accept that she might get pregnant.
I want you to take the pill.""
Yeah, okay. Sure. I wouldn't know how to raise a child afterall!
Don't take the pill. If you get pregnant, that'll be that.
Jeez, are you listening to yourself~? Do you really want us to actually end up with a child?
Well, alright then! Just take responsibility if we do, okay?
